{"tid":921513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★東江水大腸桿菌最高超標29倍","createTime":"2018-11-29T15:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T04:48:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"064eb11af87eb72ea0b1e912791fe36dc34c6688","tid":921513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2153688/org/e3618bed409d248f1d200ef1009b6b6d.jpg/kIw5raVGPxdllLMOg2mSk3TUfFwlpOvXEJOkJRCTpCU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2153688%2Forg%2Fe3618bed409d248f1d200ef1009b6b6d.jpg%2FkIw5raVGPxdllLMOg2mSk3TUfFwlpOvXEJOkJRCTpCU&h=19132688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東江水是本港最主要食水來源，但大腸桿菌量屢次超標，情況惹關注。水務諮詢委員會委會一連三日考察東江水，取得數據發現東江水的大腸桿菌含量在個別日子高達每公升6萬個，超標29倍。主席陳漢輝直斥「不能接受」（unacceptable），但他透露隨著深圳埔地嚇水質淨化廠污水處理工程將竣工，日後未經處理的污水將先淨化才排到沙灣河，東江水質將改善。<br />\n<br />\n對於有意見指本港應興建海水化淡廠，以減少依賴東江水，陳認為海水化淡廠處理量低、耗能，加上本港缺地興建，宜作後備供水方案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/265225/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%85%B8%E6%A1%BF%E8%8F%8C%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E8%B6%85%E6%A8%9929%E5%80%8D-%E6%B0%B4%E8%AB%AE%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F265225%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2585%25B8%25E6%25A1%25BF%25E8%258F%258C%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%25A8%259929%25E5%2580%258D-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597&d=%2Bh5z3WCDAK36wi5HYVrSuJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8db5076f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/265225/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%85%B8%E6%A1%BF%E8%8F%8C%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E8%B6%85%E6%